Name
       resetBusGuideMultiColors - Clears the highlighted bus guide colors

Syntax
       resetBusGuideMultiColors

       Clears the highlighted bus guide colors.

       Use  this  command  after setBusGuideMultiColors has been used to color
       the bus guide(s).

Parameters
       None

